  Designing and Deploying Microservices
  Microservices architecture makes your apps more flexible,
  more stable, and faster.  This ebook shows how to design,
  develop, and deliver microservices.
  In this ebook you will learn:
  o When and why it makes sense to adopt microservices
  o How to implement an API gateway to route traffic to microservices
  o Pros and cons of different service discovery patterns
  o Different strategies for refactoring a monolith to microservices
  https://www.nginx.com/resources/library/designing-deploying-microservices/
